---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Shutdown Agent Service"
  description="We handle your entire business shutdown for $1,000. Every form, every filing, every deadline. You sign, we execute."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-slate-800 to-red-900 px-4 py-20 text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
      <div class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-red-600/20 px-4 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-red-300">
        Full-Service Dissolution
      </div>
      <h1 class="mb-6 text-4xl font-bold leading-tight md:text-5xl">
        We Shut Down Your Business.<br />
        <span class="text-red-400">You Just Sign.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mx-auto mb-6 max-w-2xl text-lg text-slate-300">
        Filing dissolution papers is the easy part. Tax clearance, creditor notifications, EIN closure, license cancellations, final returns — that's where businesses get stuck. We handle all of it.
      </p>
      <div class="mb-8 text-5xl font-bold">$1,000<span class="text-lg font-normal text-slate-400"> flat fee</span></div>
      <a href="#get-started" class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-red-600 px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold text-white shadow-lg hover:bg-red-700">
        Get Started Now
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What's Included -->
  <section class="px-4 py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="mb-12 text-center text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">Everything That's Included</h2>
      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
        {[
          { title: 'State Dissolution Filing', desc: 'We prepare and file your Articles of Dissolution or Certificate of Cancellation with your state.' },
          { title: 'Tax Clearance Coordination', desc: 'We work with your state tax agency to obtain required clearance letters before filing.' },
          { title: 'Final Tax Return Guidance', desc: 'Step-by-step guidance on filing final federal and state tax returns with the "final return" box checked.' },
          { title: 'Creditor Notification', desc: 'We draft and send required creditor notifications per your state\'s statutory requirements.' },
          { title: 'Employee Notification', desc: 'WARN Act compliance check and employee notification templates customized to your situation.' },
          { title: 'IRS EIN Closure', desc: 'We submit the IRS letter to close your Employer Identification Number.' },
          { title: 'State Tax Account Closure', desc: 'Close your state tax accounts (income, sales, withholding) so no future filings are expected.' },
          { title: 'Business License Cancellations', desc: 'Identify and cancel all state and local business licenses and permits.' },
          { title: 'Registered Agent Termination', desc: 'Coordinate termination of registered agent service after dissolution is complete.' },
          { title: 'Certificate of Dissolution', desc: 'Obtain your official Certificate of Dissolution from the state as proof of completed shutdown.' },
          { title: 'Post-Shutdown Monitoring', desc: '90 days of monitoring for any state correspondence or compliance issues after dissolution.' },
          { title: 'Digital Asset Checklist', desc: 'Domain transfers, hosting cancellation, email forwarding, and SaaS subscription shutdown checklist.' },
        ].map(item => (
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6">
            <h3 class="mb-2 font-bold text-slate-900">{item.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">{item.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process -->
  <section class="bg-white px-4 py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="mb-12 text-center text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">How It Works</h2>
      <div class="space-y-8">
        {[
          { step: '1', title: 'Intake', desc: 'Tell us your state, entity type, and current status. We\'ll identify exactly what needs to happen.' },
          { step: '2', title: 'Audit', desc: 'We check your standing with the state, identify outstanding filings, and create your custom shutdown plan.' },
          { step: '3', title: 'Execute', desc: 'We prepare all forms, obtain tax clearance, file dissolution papers, and send required notifications.' },
          { step: '4', title: 'Verify', desc: 'We confirm dissolution with the state, obtain your certificate, and close all ancillary accounts.' },
          { step: '5', title: 'Monitor', desc: 'For 90 days after dissolution, we watch for any state correspondence and handle issues that arise.' },
        ].map(item => (
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex h-10 w-10 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-red-600 text-sm font-bold text-white">{item.step}</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900">{item.title}</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">{item.desc}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="px-4 py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="mb-8 text-center text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">Agent Service FAQ</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6">
          <h3 class="mb-2 font-bold text-slate-900">Is this legal advice?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">No. We are a filing and compliance service. We prepare and submit forms based on your state's requirements. For legal questions about liability, debts, or disputes, consult an attorney.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6">
          <h3 class="mb-2 font-bold text-slate-900">What if my business has outstanding debts?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">We can still help with the filing process, but you'll need to work with creditors or an attorney to resolve debts. We'll handle the creditor notification requirements per your state's statute.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6">
          <h3 class="mb-2 font-bold text-slate-900">How long does the full process take?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Typically 30-90 days depending on your state. Tax clearance is usually the longest step. We start filing within 48 hours of receiving your signed authorization.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6">
          <h3 class="mb-2 font-bold text-slate-900">What if I'm registered in multiple states?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">The $1,000 fee covers your home state. Each additional state where you're registered as a foreign entity is $250 for withdrawal filing.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section id="get-started" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-700 px-4 py-16 text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
      <h2 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-bold">Ready to Shut Down?</h2>
      <p class="mb-8 text-red-100">$1,000 flat fee. No hidden costs. Every filing handled. Every deadline met.</p>
      <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/9B6cN53LT1PfbRZc4Qco009" class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-white px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold text-red-600 shadow-lg hover:bg-red-50">
        Start Your Shutdown — $1,000
      </a>
      <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-red-200">Payment collected after intake call. Full refund if we can't complete your dissolution.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
